node.text: #ThirstyThursdays Raise of hands if this #StayHome period has made your skin drier and dehydrated?! #MACFixPlus to the rescue! Contains #Glycerin which is a moisture magnet 🧲, #Cucumber 🥒 & #GreenTea 🍵 extracts to soothe and calm the skin. You’ll see just how #Thirsty we #MACArtist are for it!
